{"tid":1476193,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"因支持香港民主傳遭無綫雪藏！林秀怡一腳踢撲水養家","createTime":"2019-08-15T17:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T04:55:59.000Z","uid":24516,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c93f80d0c05f9853f13f9a4d01dac59299bf8941","tid":1476193,"uid":24516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:30:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/1O6Ja9?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2F1O6Ja9%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=3f160860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/1O6Ja9?utm_source=copyshare</a><br />\n<br />\n憑無綫劇集《婚姻合伙人》光速彈起入屋的林秀怡，近日因在Instagram高調表態政治立場，即遭無綫「雪藏」，令工作量大減。走投無路下，她只好埋首其餐廳生意，以老闆娘身份繼續「撲水」，努力慳錢養家，以抵其患癌母親的龐大醫療費。<br />\n今年27歲的林秀怡入行十年，以《婚》成功打甩「綠葉」Label，劇中一幕與陸永浴缸火辣埋身「肉搏」、被對方出擒拿手「襲胸」，教人睇到津津樂道。好景不常，自從她於IG評論社會議題後，瞬間「被消失」，Out出主持了6年的音樂節目《樂勢力》之餘，又「被缺席」劇集《十二傳說》的宣傳。冇Job在身的林秀怡，去年為救母而花盡畢身積蓄，面對沉重的經濟壓力，唯一出路只能靠開業接近3年的日式西餐廳，據知餐廳已差不多回本，開始進入收成期。<br />\n<br />\n我地係唔係要去支持一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df7eb6b241e6ed16d8d2a1a0cf50aefc0865b5f","tid":1476193,"uid":15605,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:37:37.000Z","msg":"餐廳係邊去幫襯"},{"pid":"ddc9680068ef3e5104bfcd181f3d60790dd56c3f","tid":1476193,"uid":12197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:40:22.000Z","msg":"揚地址會唔會比人搞"},{"pid":"d7f6799041adc4ac0249f62c5ac34a0d5fdde4d1","tid":1476193,"uid":2974,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:40:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-foodo-旺角-多國菜-薄餅-r524117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong%2Fr-foodo-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%8B%E8%8F%9C-%E8%96%84%E9%A4%85-r52411