he chair of the influential Commons foreign affairs committee has argued. (The Guardian)//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅take返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打000000 或 N/A<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=9d67a4b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"0f0cbc96094e4737661a210630230ed2b8f0ec63","tid":1476193,"uid":28223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99852535ac4a82e81f3c0af163f3b22ff7a4883f","tid":1476193,"uid":267953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:55:19.000Z","msg":"多幫襯"},{"pid":"92ee51c7cbc11d498c5566fabc8bacb6f3cf474b","tid":1476193,"uid":291601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:58:02.000Z","msg":"好意思，借個位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">816全民㩒錢日，藍絲一齊撐</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1476207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1476207</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ba60e4ac81450995245d4e016dbd998eb2e9bbb5","tid":1476193,"uid":263809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:18:34.000Z","msg":"呢兩日就去"},{"pid":"9499d2a7b2468f281111e98fa9e028e9af7e68d3","tid":1476193,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:18:59.000Z","msg":"支持去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 